The LfReactor library based on poco c++ libraries
This library implement leader/followers pattern with reactor pattern

ATTENTION!
==========
Before building the source code, you should the poco c++'s Foundation
library and Net library well. you should configure the poco c++ libraries
environment well.More details please see poco c++ library's README

BUILDING ON LINUX
=================
You can use codeblocks open the LfReactor.workspace file to build it

BUILDING ON WINDOWS
===================
You can use visual studio 9.0(2008) to open the LfReactor9.sln to build it
or you can use the higher version ide to build it

enjoy it
